#define HT_TRY ( _s_,
_code_   ) 

Value:

do { \
  try { _code_; } \
  catch (Exception &e) { HT_THROW2(e.code(), e, _s_); } \
  catch (std::bad_alloc &e) { \
    HT_THROW(Error::EXTERNAL, "bad alloc " _s_); \
  } \
  catch (std::exception &e) { \
    HT_THROWF(Error::EXTERNAL, "External exception " _s_ ": %s",  e.what()); \
  } \
} while (0)
